text: Jönköping is a city in Sweden. About 90,000 people live there. It is in southern Sweden near the lake Vättern. Jönköping was actually 3 towns that grew into one large town. The 3 towns were, Jönköping (55.000), Huskvarna (22.000) and Norrahammar (9.000). Jönköping is the 9th biggest city in Sweden. == Sports == * HV71, ice hockey club * Jönköping Bandy IF, bandy club * Jönköpings IK, floor ball club * Jönköpings Södra IF, soccer club ==References== ==Other websites==
